 ---
 
 FINDPEAK  - find local maxima in an image
 -----
 
 
 Usage:
 ------
 findpeak img=image [rmatch=rmatch] [rmin=rmin] [rmax=rmax] [o=outfile] \
                [threshold=threshold]
 	
  	rmatch    -- minimum distance (pix) between sources (def: 1)   
  	rmin and rmax are inner edges of the image region to be used
  	o         -- write to a file instead of STDOUT
  	threshold -- detection threshold (def: no default)
 ---
